title: S16 Ep146: Supernatural News/Parashare: Nostradamus Knows Edition w/ Mallie Fox
itunes:title: Supernatural News/Parashare: Nostradamus Knows Edition w/ Mallie Fox
description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Nostradamus Knows Edition with  Guest, Mallie Fox!

As we begin closing out the year we examine Nostradamus predictions that came true in 2021 and look ahead to what he saw for 2022! Who is ready for a ride on Elon's Ark? An Ultrasound reveals a touching portrait of a Grandpa and new grandchild, we encounter the Windsor Werewolf and more!
